<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>观点文 on 📖 爱分享读书</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/categories/%E8%A7%82%E7%82%B9%E6%96%87/</link><description>Recent content in 观点文 on 📖 爱分享读书</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 04:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ishareread.com/categories/%E8%A7%82%E7%82%B9%E6%96%87/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>朱光潜的活法：万事只求半称心</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E6%9C%B1%E5%85%89%E6%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E6%B4%BB%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%8B%E5%8F%AA%E6%B1%82%E5%8D%8A%E7%A7%B0%E5%BF%83/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 04:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E6%9C%B1%E5%85%89%E6%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E6%B4%BB%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%8B%E5%8F%AA%E6%B1%82%E5%8D%8A%E7%A7%B0%E5%BF%83/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://www.ishareread.com/" alt="Featured image of post 朱光潜的活法：万事只求半称心" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;春天来了，你有没有这种感觉？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;明明窗外花开正好，阳光温柔地洒在书页上，你却坐在工位前，对着电脑屏幕发呆。脑子里装着太多事——房贷还没还完、孩子的兴趣班费用该交了、下周的述职报告还没写完……心里头乱糟糟的，像有只猫在挠。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>库克退休这堂课：为什么基业长青比成为首富更难？</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E5%BA%93%E5%85%8B%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E8%BF%99%E5%A0%82%E8%AF%BE%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%9F%BA%E4%B8%9A%E9%95%BF%E9%9D%92%E6%AF%94%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E9%A6%96%E5%AF%8C%E6%9B%B4%E9%9A%BE/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 20:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E5%BA%93%E5%85%8B%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E8%BF%99%E5%A0%82%E8%AF%BE%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%9F%BA%E4%B8%9A%E9%95%BF%E9%9D%92%E6%AF%94%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E9%A6%96%E5%AF%8C%E6%9B%B4%E9%9A%BE/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://www.ishareread.com/" alt="Featured image of post 库克退休这堂课：为什么基业长青比成为首富更难？" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;4月21日，苹果官宣了一条震动全球科技圈的消息：执掌苹果15年的蒂姆·库克，将于今年9月正式卸任CEO，转任董事会执行董事长。硬件工程高级副总裁约翰·特努斯接棒，成为苹果第八任CEO。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>为什么你读了很多书，依然过不好这一生？</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%BB%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%B9%A6%E4%BE%9D%E7%84%B6%E8%BF%87%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%80%E7%94%9F/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 20:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%BB%E4%BA%86%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%B9%A6%E4%BE%9D%E7%84%B6%E8%BF%87%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%80%E7%94%9F/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://www.ishareread.com/" alt="Featured image of post 为什么你读了很多书，依然过不好这一生？" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;你有没有过这样的时刻？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;书架上的书越堆越高，手机里收藏的文章越来越多，报名的课程一个接一个。每年年初给自己定下&amp;quot;读50本书&amp;quot;的目标，年底复盘时发现自己真的读完了51本。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>